  <brief_title>Clinical and Stereoradiological Comparison of the Results After Primary Cemented Total Knee Arthroplasty Inserted With or Without the Use of a Tourniquet</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical and Stereoradiological Comparison of the Results After Primary TKA Inserted With or Without the Use of a Tourniquet</official_title>
