  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate if the use of a tourniquet during insertion of a
      cemented primary total knee arthroplasty will influence clinical and radiological (measured
      with RSA X-ray technique) outcome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
